    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SKAZ：沙皇之影</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款关于记忆、意志与古罗斯神话的氛围动作角色扮演游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358780/extras/a9aa472b5d430ee41061d839995ca30c.poster.avif?t=1764701923\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358780/extras/a9aa472b5d430ee41061d839995ca30c.webm?t=1764701923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>SKAZ：沙皇之影</strong>》灵感源于斯拉夫神话与原创世界观。<br>“大崩落”之后，世界支离破碎：<strong>现实界、冥界、圣界与幻界</strong>彼此交融，古老传说重新降临人间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在毫无姓名与记忆的状态中醒来——<br>在一个<strong>记忆已成为货币</strong>的世界。<br>你的选择不仅决定结局，也塑造角色的性格、力量，以及世界对你的回应方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 四界之境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索<strong>现实界、冥界、圣界与幻界</strong>——每一界都有独特的景观、生灵与法则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358780/extras/2ebe6355ae98274759b0b0741621916c.avif?t=1764701923\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358780/extras/b17b57133f3542131a4b3f61b5a5aa70.avif?t=1764701923\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 记忆即规则</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你选择<strong>遗忘</strong>或<strong>保留</strong>的部分，将深刻影响你的玩法与角色成长方向。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 战术战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面怪物、灵体与堕落诸神的残影。<br>运用仪式、咒术与独特技能击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358780/extras/03a1ef162ba2e90882ca5986505ff9d0.avif?t=1764701923\" width=1456 height=816 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 代价之人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将遇见：<br>• <strong>面包精灵商人</strong>——交易梦境与灵魂的神秘旅者<br>• <strong>水妖</strong>——讥讽而危险的深渊守卫者<br>• <strong>受古誓束缚的巫者与冥界生灵</strong><br>• <strong>基捷什</strong>——那座自深处再度现身的传说之城</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358780/extras/f1c2ca740b47d7f275d790e74e7c360b.avif?t=1764701923\" width=1456 height=816 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 独特作者风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斯拉夫黑暗奇幻氛围，手绘画风，奇迹与恐惧在古罗斯的阴影中并存。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ <strong>重拾自我</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界遗忘你之前，找回属于你的名字。</p>",
